  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nOn NodeJS v18 (merged in https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/4779) Buffer.concat got more expensive.\r\n- Reported by our performance tracker https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/commit/7d662d7951db27edcee15fd7266bed322f0a3882#commitcomment-92810061\r\n- Upstream issue https://github.com/nodejs/node/issues/45802\r\n\r\nWe decided to accept the regression for now to unblock v18. But must review and consider and mitigate when possible",
